sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_048_1_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Reservation of a Connector - Faulted
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.17.1 - Reservation of a Connector
    Note over CP,CS: Doc ref: Table 168, Page 144/176 (2025-11)
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Reservation feature profile

    CS->>CP: 1. ReserveNow.req
    Note right of CS: CS Validation:<br/>connectorId = <Configured ConnectorId><br/>idTag = <Configured Valid IdTag>

    CP-->>CS: 2. ReserveNow.conf (status: Faulted)
    Note over CP: CP Validation: status must be Faulted

    Note over CP,CS: Expected (CS): Accepts the Reservation<br/>message with the not Accepted status
